
Open Loop (preventive)
 - source control (token bucket, leaky bucket)
 - destination control

Closed Loop (reactive)
 - implicit feedback (packet dropped) 
 - explicit feedback (message sent to source) 
   - persistent(global) (constant feedback irrespective of congestion)
   - responsive
     - global
     - local

     Examples of closed loop
     PID controler
     Admission control
     Load shedding
     Slow strat

